---
title: One-Pot Mexican Quinoa
description: You won’t be left with a pile of dishes after this easy one-pot meal. We’ve combined quinoa, black beans, diced tomatoes, and corn for a satisfying Mexican-inspired meal. For a touch of richness, creamy avocado and tangy feta finish o  the dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-mexican-quinoa-1055fd1c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/one-pot-mexican-quinoa-27590f3c.pdf
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
